OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772971377
OL,3,CMan who posted pro-Isis propaganda on
OL,4,Csocial media jailed for five years
OL,6,FA man who posted propaganda for the so-
OL,7,Fcalled Islamic State group on social
OL,8,Fmedia has been jailed for five years.
OL,10,FShazad Ali, 21, of Newport, south
OL,11,FWales, published hundreds of videos on
OL,12,FInstagram and TikTok in a bid to
OL,13,Fpromote the terrorist organisation.
OL,15,FBristol Crown Court heard Ali
OL,16,Finterspersed material in support of
OL,17,Fthe group with footage of Pride
OL,18,Fmarches and martial arts to deceive
OL,19,Falgorithms on the social media
OL,20,Fplatforms.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772971377
OL,3,CMan who posted pro-Isis propaganda on
OL,4,Csocial media jailed for five years
OL,6,FHe created chats on Telegram which
OL,7,Fwere used to discuss Isis and involved
OL,8,Fpeople he believed were members of the
OL,9,Fgroup, the court was told.
OL,11,FIn one exchange, Ali told a 17-year-
OL,12,Fold boy that he would be "the next
OL,13,Fspokesman for Dawla in Wales" `
OL,14,Freferring to al-Dawla al-Islamiya fi
OL,15,Fal-Iraq al-Sham, meaning the Islamic
OL,16,FState in Iraq and the Levant.
OL,18,FAli was arrested in January last year
OL,19,Fafter authorities identified pro-Isis
OL,20,Fcontent on his social media accounts.
OL,26,@tD@ZOUuD@]O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/13
