OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772971377
OL,3,CMan who posted pro-Isis propaganda on
OL,4,Csocial media jailed for five years
OL,6,FHe later pleaded guilty to four
OL,7,Fcharges contrary to the Terrorism Act
OL,8,F` supporting a proscribed
OL,9,Forganisation, two counts of
OL,10,Fencouraging terrorism and one of
OL,11,Fpossessing a document likely to be
OL,12,Fuseful to a terrorist.
OL,14,FThe prosecution offered no evidence
OL,15,Fagainst Ali on charges he was a member
OL,16,Fof Isis and that he possessed a second
OL,17,Fdocument about explosives.
OL,19,FJudge Parker directed not guilty
OL,20,Fverdicts in respect of those charges.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
