PN,46304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772971377
OL,3,CMan who posted pro-Isis propaganda on
OL,4,Csocial media jailed for five years
OL,6,FJudge Christopher Parker KC jailed Ali
OL,7,Fto five years in custody and an
OL,8,Fadditional two years on licence upon
OL,9,Fhis release.
OL,11,FHe told Ali he hoped he would return
OL,12,Fto the "ordinary, happy life which
OL,13,Fyour parents so long for you" after
OL,14,Fbeing deradicalised.
OL,26,@tD@HOUuD@]O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/13
