FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772971377
OL,3,CMan who posted pro-Isis propaganda on
OL,4,Csocial media jailed for five years
OL,6,F"Between July 2024 and January 2025,
OL,7,Fyou became immersed in the doctrine
OL,8,Fand aims of Isis, a terrorist
OL,9,Forganisation seeking to establish a
OL,10,Fcaliphate through violence of the most
OL,11,Fextreme and horrendous kind," Judge
OL,12,FParker said.
OL,14,F"Over that period, you spent much if
OL,15,Fnot all of your time in your bedroom,
OL,16,Fon your telephone, developing your
OL,17,Finterest in and promotion of Isis.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@]O]vD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772971377
OL,3,CMan who posted pro-Isis propaganda on
OL,4,Csocial media jailed for five years
OL,6,F"You came into contact with a person
OL,7,Fcalled Abu Qatada, someone who you
OL,8,Fbelieved to be a member of Isis who
OL,9,Fwas fighting the Taliban in
OL,10,FAfghanistan.
OL,12,F"You were to assert your actions were
OL,13,Fundertaken under pressure from that
OL,14,Fman. The investigations of your
OL,15,Fdevices reveal there was no such
OL,16,Fpressure."
OL,18,FThe judge said Ali acted as a
OL,19,F"gatekeeper" to Abu Qatada and vetted
OL,20,Fthose wishing to access chats in which
OL,21,Fhe was a participant.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@JO]{D@AOU{D@LO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
