OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772971377
OL,3,CMan who posted pro-Isis propaganda on
OL,4,Csocial media jailed for five years
OL,6,FHe described how Ali had exchanged
OL,7,F1,700 messages with a 17-year-old boy
OL,8,Fover a two-month period in attempts to
OL,9,Frecruit him to Isis from Al-Qaeda.
OL,11,F"In addition, through online
OL,12,Fcommunication you were able to recruit
OL,13,Fsix men into the ranks of Isis," the
OL,14,Fjudge said.
OL,16,FThe judge said Ali had created
OL,17,Fpropaganda videos by disguising
OL,18,F"violent" imagery in support of Isis
OL,19,Fwith innocent footage of mixed martial
OL,20,Farts and Pride events.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@`O]zD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
