OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772971377
OL,3,CMan who posted pro-Isis propaganda on
OL,4,Csocial media jailed for five years
OL,6,F"That exercise required you to
OL,7,Fcollect, generate, edit and publish
OL,8,Fthe footage," he told Ali. "Acting as
OL,9,Fa recruiter and propagandist was
OL,10,Falready harmful and dangerous. You
OL,11,Fthen engaged in a closed Telegram chat
OL,12,Fgroup you had set up called Lone
OL,13,FWolves with 11 members."
OL,15,FA document, providing instructions on
OL,16,Fhow to make an explosive, was posted
OL,17,Fin that chat group and downloaded
OL,18,Fautomatically onto Ali's device.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@MO]pD@\OUuD@XO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/13
