PN,46309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772971377
OL,3,CMan who posted pro-Isis propaganda on
OL,4,Csocial media jailed for five years
OL,6,FWhen another participant on the group
OL,7,Fasked how to get the ingredients to
OL,8,Fmake the explosive, Ali replied: "If
OL,9,Ffrom the UK, I have them all, I can
OL,10,Fsend."
OL,12,FThe judge, who described the incident
OL,13,Fas an "escalation in your behaviour
OL,14,Fand involvement", noted that none of
OL,15,Fthe chemicals were discovered despite
OL,16,Fextensive searches at Ali's family
OL,17,Fhome.Prosecuting, Christopher Amis
OL,18,Fsaid Ali had given interviews to
OL,19,Fpolice after his arrest ` telling
OL,20,Fofficers he had been born Muslim but
OL,21,Fdid not practise his faith until 2023.
OL,26,@pD@bOUrD@FO]uD@GOUvD@PO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/13
