PN,46310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772971377
OL,3,CMan who posted pro-Isis propaganda on
OL,4,Csocial media jailed for five years
OL,6,FAli told police he played online games
OL,7,Fsuch as Roblox and through this was
OL,8,Fintroduced to Abu Qatada, who was a
OL,9,Fmember of Isis living in Afghanistan.
OL,11,FDuring one TikTok chat, Ali claimed he
OL,12,Fworked to create media for Isis which
OL,13,F"reinforces the notion the defendant
OL,14,Fwas working as an influencer and
OL,15,Fpropagandist for Isis", Mr Amis said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@VO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/13
