PN,46311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772971377
OL,3,CMan who posted pro-Isis propaganda on
OL,4,Csocial media jailed for five years
OL,6,FMr Amis played three videos taken from
OL,7,FAli's social media to the court, one
OL,8,Fof which featured Mohammed Emwazi `
OL,9,Faka Jihadi John ` holding a scalpel
OL,10,Fand a knife while audio spoke of
OL,11,F"slaughter".
OL,13,FThe barrister said it was not possible
OL,14,Fto say how many videos Ali posted
OL,15,Fonline but it was "certainly in the
OL,16,Fhundreds".
OL,18,FRepresenting Ali, Jodie-Jane Hitchcock
OL,19,Fsaid he had a "very modest number of
OL,20,Ffollowers" on his accounts and was
OL,21,Fsocially isolated.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@KO]wD@SOUxD@IO]{D@OOU|D@JO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
