OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772971377
OL,3,CMan who posted pro-Isis propaganda on
OL,4,Csocial media jailed for five years
OL,6,F"He found himself exposed to a world
OL,7,Fonline where his isolation was
OL,8,Fexploited and he found an outlet," she
OL,9,Fsaid, adding that he was remorseful
OL,10,Ffor his actions.
OL,12,FSpeaking after the case, Detective
OL,13,FChief Inspector Leanne Williams, of
OL,14,FCounter Terrorism Police Wales,
OL,15,Fdescribed Ali as representing a "very
OL,16,Fclear, very dangerous threat to the
OL,17,Fpublic".
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@bO]wD@aOUyD@GO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/13
