PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772971377
OL,3,CMan who posted pro-Isis propaganda on
OL,4,Csocial media jailed for five years
OL,6,F"Ali visibly expressed his support for
OL,7,Fthe Islamic State and it was our
OL,8,Foverriding priority to ensure the
OL,9,Fpublic were protected from both him
OL,10,Fand the abhorrent rhetoric he
OL,11,Fpromoted," she said.
